{"tid":1467814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全部話我地今日輸左既冷氣軍師同我入嚟！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:48:05.000Z","uid":34453,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18883ef80140cfa3711583293bdd8d77095c42bf","tid":1467814,"uid":34453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:14.000Z","msg":"其實係同所有人講<br />\n<br />\n冇錯 今日阻遊客呢步 絕對係失大於得<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">但你有冇諗過前線點解行呢一步？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家都想為件事好 經歷琴晩無啦啦散水之後個個梗係想做多啲等效果勁啲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點知會搞到咁？佢地想？</span><br />\n<br />\n唔做都做咗 唔應該錯都錯咗<br />\n有邊個未錯過？現場個個可以mon實live同tg？唔洗做？<br />\n如果每一步都做啱 我哋晨早贏咗喇！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">做錯決定唔係問題<br />\n只要以後唔再犯同樣既錯就得</span><br />\n<br />\n我地可以由6月9打到而家 靠既係我地既堅持同不斷進步<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而唔係互相指責</span>"},{"pid":"663295a026d5aa473f61302a0f9cf4da7441ad9e","tid":1467814,"uid":34453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:08.000Z","msg":"我地而家要做嘅係團結一致<br />\n一齊諗下一次要點樣先做得更加好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港加油</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">機場仲有得打 唔好咁快放棄</span>"},{"pid":"a016d0cebbba7fe996d5b9d8a055576d778d8a04","tid":1467814,"uid":34453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:18.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"8f5d2c89ea50b6961b8435f223f1e41012dad162","tid":1467814,"uid":210280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:39.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"b754f6a5853bef6d71b2cb2d1b26119e1319ed9b","tid":1467814,"uid":60393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:39.000Z","msg":"轉發 可做reference <br />\n問：阻塞機場搞死香港？<br />\n答：「做法不完美，但可接受，要改善。」<br />\n<br />\n問：點解阻止公安離開？<br />\n答：「佢唔喺現場出現就冇事，去得果度就可能有呢啲風險。」<br />\n<br />\n問：阻止救護帶佢離開？人命嚟㗎。<br />\n答：「而家眾說紛云，我認為事主可以去報警先，警方必定會跟進調查。」<br />\n<br />\n問：點解你地咁冇人性，濫用暴力，究竟想點？<br />\n「在場嘅市民只係用最低武力，當一切平靜後，真誠對話就會展開。」<br />\n<br />\n對唔住，7.21、8.11血仍未乾，有人爆頭，有人失明，有人俾黑警打到成地血都冇收手，之後我從來冇聽過，警方有道歉有撤查。<br />\n<br />\n以上，全部係黑警同林奠嘅對白，香港人已經好克制了。<br />\n<br />\n人命？你睇俾黑警打到成地血嘅義士個樣，同埋呢個公安？現場有一句，喺大陸，你死撚咗啦。<br />\n<br />\n信焉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#不割席<br />\n#不篤灰<br />\n#不分化<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/603037573183215/posts/1346089382211360?s=100001644574516&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F603037573183215%2Fposts%2F1346089382211360%3Fs%3D100001644574516%26sfns%3Dmo&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ijzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=083ee53a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/603037573183215/posts/1346089382211360?s=100001644574516&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"94d9e078663c583287fb1e7638769403bd0efcf1","tid":1467814,"uid":34453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:57.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"1657a0b60c9434d76f98f636f887bd881e9db73b","tid":1467814,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:12.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n【跪求大家入黎睇下，我好想香港贏】關於鬼關於衝動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466732</a>"},{"pid":"08d132ed7d56d8bb8b248ada0cf32e6b2a72d9ce","tid":1467814,"uid":34453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bae6cfcbf759819ed3448dd7703b9b51ca0b48eb","tid":1467814,"uid":34453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:55.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"6a0ac2067327270fb4b13c261e544cd7ad28de20","tid":1467814,"uid":34453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"7c009495b94a169d3ca3692741a1363de8cc24d0","tid":1467814,"uid":34453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:23.000Z","msg":"再再推！"},{"pid":"d810e0d3f9b89eb70808d20a125d30b3c1549